Personal vimrc on top of vundle (a Vim plugin manager) 

Quick setup

1. Make dir for plugins in $HOME/.vim
   $ mkdir ~/.vim/bundle
2. Setup Vundle
   $ git clone git://github.com/gmarik/Vundle.vim.git ~/.vim/bundle/Vundle.vim
3. Install plugins inside vim by 
   : PluginInstall
4. Make vimproc
   $ cd ~/.vim/bundle/vimproc.vim
   $ make 

Known issue
1. plugin 'vim-colors-solarized', colorscheme solarized.vim can't be found. 
   walkaround: copy solarized.vim into ~/.vim/colors 
  
   
